 2024-02562024-03-25AAFC
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder authorizing to enter into agreement with the provinces of Nova Scotia, New Brunswick and Prince Edward Island to establish a livestock price insurance program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an AGREEMENT with Nova Scotia, New Brunswick and Prince Edward Island to expand the Livestock Price Insurance program to those provinces to provide cattle producers in those provinces with access to protection against unanticipated price declines.
AttachmentsAttachment
